          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card challenge-card-v2 deliver-card-with-bg reveal reveal-d2" style="background-image: url('/images/detail-ai.webp');">
          <div class="service-detail-card__content">
            <h3><a href="/geo-agency-singapore/">GEO (AI Search Optimisation)</a></h3>
            <p>Get cited when homeowners ask ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, or Google AI Mode for "best interior designer for HDB renovation." Same citation playbook we've used for our own agency.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card challenge-card-v2 deliver-card-with-bg reveal reveal-d3" style="background-image: url('/images/detail-google-ads.webp');">
          <div class="service-detail-card__content">
            <h3><a href="/interior-designer-google-ads-singapore/">Google Ads for ID Firms</a></h3>
            <p>High-intent campaigns timed to BTO key-collection seasons. GCLID tracking from click to signed contract. Industry benchmark CPL: S$30–S$80.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card challenge-card-v2 deliver-card-with-bg reveal reveal-d1" style="background-image: url('/images/detail-reels-video.webp');">
          <div class="service-detail-card__content">
            <h3><a href="/interior-designer-social-media-singapore/">Social Media for ID Firms</a></h3>
            <p>The Renovation Reel Formula — 30s walkthrough Reels, 60s design-process TikToks, Instagram and Facebook content. Built for how SG homeowners actually scroll.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card challenge-card-v2 deliver-card-with-bg reveal reveal-d2" style="background-image: url('/images/detail-graphic-design.webp');">
          <div class="service-detail-card__content">
            <h3><a href="/interior-designer-branding-singapore/">Branding for ID Firms</a></h3>
            <p>The brand system that differentiates you from the 50 other ID firms in your catchment. Logo, palette, portfolio template, photo direction — positioned by niche.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card challenge-card-v2 deliver-card-with-bg reveal reveal-d3" style="background-image: url('/images/detail-business-website.webp');">
          <div class="service-detail-card__content">
            <h3><a href="/interior-design-website-singapore/">Portfolio Websites for ID Firms</a></h3>
