            <p>Interior design is a visual category. We treat your completed projects as the marketing asset they are — shot lists, format-by-format reformatting, before-after framing, and integration into your portfolio site.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-detail-card challenge-card-v2 reveal reveal-d2">
